{"tid":1562384,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"北九州好玩定南九州好玩","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T19:02:46.000Z","uid":89538,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"eecd61c3ffb478fee958af05269e444a1a768a38","tid":1562384,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"心大心細<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熊本同由布院最想去 但係中間<br />\n唔知跟南玩定北玩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06cbac8d8402ad805f29b4f819172adb19f724b","tid":1562384,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6255b867b7cbc616a31f275b89924dafae72de3c","tid":1562384,"uid":124241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:17:59.000Z","msg":"睇你鍾意玩咩囉<br />\n<br />\n我覺得北九州就行街，睇景都有，交通方便，野食好多，同日本平時大城市差唔多，去遠少少近郊都方便<br />\n<br />\n而南九州去既地方就散少少，車程耐少少，交通班次冇咁密，睇景會多啲，所以人都會少好多"},{"pid":"09263b9b9c04fc245cf41bd6bfcb4445674d815f","tid":1562384,"uid":124241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"而你講嗰2個地方通常都癡住北九州玩，熊本其實係九州中間，坐JR 都好似2個鐘，油布就stay 一日浸溫泉，一條長直街行到尾"},{"pid":"db63ee520a727b23